CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 30, 1958, pg. 32 reads: "Joe's Just Looking - Former world heavyweight champion Joe Louis, right, is nothing more than an interested spectator at the annual United Golfers Association tournament being played at North Park this week. However, two golfers who have competed against Louis regularly in past, are playing.  At left is Pittsburgh-born singer Billy Eckstine.  In the center is Leroy Tyrus, St. Louis (Mo.) politician."
TitMainTitle: Billy Eckstine, Leroy Tyrus, and Joe Louis gathered on North Park golf course for UGA tournament
